<item>
            <title>[DATACMNS-181] page.page=3&amp;page.size=30 and  @PageableDefaults(pageNumber = 3, value = 30) don&apos;t return the same page.</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATACMNS-181</link>
                <project id="10510" key="DATACMNS">Spring Data Commons</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This problem happens in PageableArgumentResolver &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The default has is really 3+1 because of these lines in getDefaultFromAnnotationOrFallback:&lt;br/&gt;
// +1 is because we substract 1 later&lt;br/&gt;
return new PageRequest(defaults.pageNumber() + 1, defaults.value());&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This +1/-1 stuff is making using this code very confusing.&lt;br/&gt;
page.page=1 will return the same results at page.page=0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
